item.title: CVE-2019-6658|2024-08-04T20:31:02.522Z -- f5 -- big-ip%20%28afm%29
item.description: On BIG-IP AFM 15.0.0-15.0.1, 14.0.0-14.1.2, 13.1.0-13.1.3.1, and 12.1.0-12.1.5, a vulnerability in the AFM configuration utility may allow any authenticated BIG-IP user to run an SQL injection attack.
